   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Create a new email or open an existing email.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Load the X-Author Chatter Online add-in by doing one of the following:</p>
            <ol>
               <li>
                  <p>If you are creating a new email message, click the <uicontrol>Add-ins</uicontrol> icon at the top of the message window and choose <uicontrol>Ink Outlook Online</uicontrol> from the task pane to the right. X-Author opens inside the task pane.</p>
                  <p>
                     <p>/screenshot/</p>
                  </p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>If you are opening an existing email, click the <uicontrol>Ink Outlook Online</uicontrol> app link just below the recipient line of the email message. X-Author opens in a separate pane below the link.</p>
                  <p>
                     <p>/screenshot/</p>
                  </p>
               </li>
            </ol>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Connect to X-Author Chatter Online as described in <xref href="../connecting_to_x_author_ch_40370449/40370449.xml" format="dita">Connecting to X-Author Chatter Online</xref>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select who you want to collaborate with in your Chatter feed by clicking one of the icons:</p>
            <p>
               <p>
                  <table>
                     <tgroup cols="2">
                        <tbody>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>/Chatter icon/</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Your audience will be everyone in your organization with a Chatter account.</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>/Group icon/</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Your audience will be all the members of the group you select.</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>/Individual icon/</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Your audience will be the single individual you select.</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                        </tbody>
                     </tgroup>
                  </table>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Choose how you want to share content to Chatter.</p>
            <p>
               <p>/screenshot of chatter window and drop-down/</p>
               <p>
                  <table>
                     <tgroup cols="2">
                        <tbody>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Post</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Enter a comment to solicit feedback, while not copying any content from the body of the email or email attachments.</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Selected Content</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Not supported.</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Selected Slides</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Not supported.</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Entire Presentation</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Not supported.</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                        </tbody>
                     </tgroup>
                  </table>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Share</uicontrol> to add your comments to the Chatter feed.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
